#, fuzzy
msgid "bombkit1_pre_txt"
msgstr ""
"사령관님, we've recovered a dangerous new alien pistol that seems to fire high-energy particle beams -- more deadly than lasers, more accurate than plasma weapons, and an extremely nasty new threat to our troops on the battlefield. Preliminary tests against our armour have produced distressing results. We need to perform more research on these weapons immediately.\n"
